### If You Are in Crisis

If you are experiencing a mental health crisis, suicidal thoughts, severe anxiety, or any other emergency:

**STOP using ADHD-OS immediately and contact emergency services:**
- **US:** Call 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) or 911
- **International:** Contact your local emergency services or crisis hotline
- **Crisis Text Line:** Text HOME to 741741

Do not rely on ADHD-OS or any software for crisis support. Seek immediate professional help.

### Informed Consent

Your use of ADHD-OS constitutes your informed consent to these terms. You acknowledge that:
- You have read and understood this disclaimer
- You are not using ADHD-OS as a substitute for professional medical care
- You accept all risks associated with ADHD-OS use
- You will discontinue use and seek professional help if you experience negative effects
- You have consulted with or are under the care of health professionals for ADHD management

